data.description: This residence offers an appealing blend of craftsmanship, making it an ideal choice for investors and first-time home buyers seeking a valuable estate opportunity. This is the right pick! The brick front is traditional, with a formal living room, dining room, and sunroom. The kitchen features plenty of cabinet space, stone counters, an island, a breakfast nook, a wall oven & microwave, and a gas cooktop. Oversized master suite with sitting room. Full semi-finished basement with kitchen, full bath, and rooms galore. There's even an exterior walkway to the basement. 2 HVAC units. The home is much larger than what's indicated on tax records. 20 minutes from downtown Atlanta, 20 minutes from Whole Foods, and 35 minutes to Buckhead. Selling AS IS.
